{"article_id":"2ShDJ3gnINiqU056","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump proposed $ 4.4 trillion in spending cuts over the next decade in his budget for fiscal year 2021 -","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"a document","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"that is expected to be quickly dismissed by the Democratic-controlled House of Representatives .","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"The proposal included slashing foreign aid by 21 % .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"Budget chief Russell Vought said","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"the White House wants to boost funding for the U.S. International Development Finance Corporation","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"while cutting other types of foreign aid .","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"`` Our view is that we have trillion-dollar deficits","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"as far","depth":12},{"id":9,"text":"as the eye can see ,","depth":12},{"id":10,"text":"and we have to take care of our deficits","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"and those numbers need to get down , ''","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"Vought said in an interview with NPR 's Steve Inskeep .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"Trump has proposed massive cuts to aid in each of his budget proposals .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"Congress ,","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"which holds the power of the purse ,","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"has ignored those past requests .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"`` Democrats in Congress have opposed his previous budgets .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"We hope","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"that changes .","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"We probably need to have a national election","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"before it does , ''","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"Vought said .","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"The proposed foreign aid cuts immediately drew fire from retired Adm. Mike Mullen ,","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"who was chairman of the Joint Chiefs of Staff from 2007 to 2011 .","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"`` The more we cut the international affairs budget ,","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"the higher the risk for longer and deadlier military operations , ''","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"Mullen said in a letter to congressional leaders .","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"The $ 4.875 trillion budget highlighted Trump 's priorities on border security , tax cuts , space exploration and other policies","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"he may pursue","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"if he wins a second term in the November presidential election .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"Veterans Affairs and NASA were the biggest winners ,","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"while the EPA and Army Corps of Engineers saw big declines .","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"The largest declines were seen at the Commerce Department","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"- that 's because the 2020 census will have concluded ,","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"accounting for the drawdown in spending .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"Trump 's political rivals are expected to scour the budget for details","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"they can brandish on the campaign trail","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"- particularly any signs","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"that Trump wants to cut mandatory spending on safety net programs such as Medicare and Social Security .","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"Trump was asked in a CNBC interview last month","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"whether cuts to `` entitlements '' would ever be considered .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"`` At some point they will be .","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"We have tremendous growth , ''","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"Trump said .","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"`` And at the right time , we will take a look at that . ''","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"On Saturday , Trump said on Twitter","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"that this was not the right time .","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"`` We 're not touching Medicare ,","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"we want to keep Medicare ,","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"we 're not touching Social Security , ''","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"Trump told governors at the White House on Monday .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"`` We 're not decreasing Medicaid","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"but we 're doing a lot of things","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"that are very good","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"including [ addressing ]","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"waste and fraud , ''","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"The White House and Congress negotiated a two-year spending deal last year","depth":5},{"id":59,"text":"that sets overall spending numbers for 2020 and 2021 , another factor","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"that will curb Trump 's ambitions .","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"The budget envisions $ 135 billion in savings for prescription drugs in the Medicare program ,","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"Vought said ,","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"a signal","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"the White House hopes","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"Congress can agree on a plan","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"to lower drug prices .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"The House passed a bill in December ,","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"which the White House promptly rejected .","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"Trump has praised a plan","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"proposed by Republican Sen. Chuck Grassley and the Senate Finance Committee .","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"But so far , Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell has not endorsed it .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"Budget hawks have long urged curbs on spending","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"- particularly on the big-ticket entitlement programs -","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"to address the debt and deficit .","depth":5},{"id":76,"text":"Trump promised to eliminate the U.S. debt in eight years","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"when he was first elected .","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"But his budget comes","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"as the nonpartisan Congressional Budget Office estimated","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"government spending outpaced revenues by about $ 900 billion in 2019","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"and said","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"the deficit will balloon to more than $ 1 trillion each year","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"beginning in 2022 .","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"Trump 's new budget proposal projects","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"that the deficit can be trimmed by $ 4.6 trillion over a decade","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"and sees a balanced budget possible in 15 years ,","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"Vought said .","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"That relies on the economy growing at 2.8 % this year and 3 % thereafter","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"- growth","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"that exceeds the outlook from the Federal Reserve , Congressional Budget Office and private forecasters .","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"Actual GDP growth was 2.9 % in 2018","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"and slowed to 2.3 % in 2019 .","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"NPR chief economics correspondent Scott Horsley contributed to this story .","depth":1}],"relations":[{"parent":187,"left":186,"right":93,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":186,"left":151,"right":185,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":121,"right":150,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":116,"right":120,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116,"left":106,"right":115,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":96,"right":105,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":96,"left":0,"right":95,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":95,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":3,"right":104,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":98,"right":103,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":4,"right":97,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":97,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":103,"left":102,"right